displayProperties.name: 惊颤竞速
displayProperties.description: Sam Moleyn says they have a thing called "Skee-Ball," and with enough points, you can win prizes. Ghost really wants to come back when things "calm down."

displayProperties.name: 水培区
displayProperties.description: 暗影军团摧毁了一座重要的水培农场设施，这座设施是内欧姆那人民食物来源之一，把那座设施夺回来。

displayProperties.name: 镀金箴言
displayProperties.description:
"What is the Earth idiom? Through a... mirror?"
Forbidden tradition. The Shadow Legion want to fight, so fight them.

displayProperties.name: 救赎花园
displayProperties.description: 花园向你发出了召唤。果断回应，谨慎行事。

displayProperties.name: 深岩墓室
displayProperties.description: 传承的锁链必须被打破。

displayProperties.name: 门徒誓约
displayProperties.description: 进入萨瓦图恩王座世界的泥沼地中潜伏的金字塔飞船，探索深藏的黑暗秘密。

displayProperties.name: 梦魇根源
displayProperties.description: 一个邪恶的威胁扎根于此。
